First race with the team, maybe a bit of race craft and experience missing but killer teamspirit and motivation to learn will definitely bring some improvement! 💪 Concerning myself, I'm feeling better in the races but there's still lots of room for improvement though... Had a good day at improving myself too, 30km to the race, 90km race and 65km extra to call it a week! ✅ also really stocked with my first +500km week since June (559km to be precise) 🤓 only good times ahead!
