New year, new goals, new races, new team!
Happy to be joining @teamciclesvic for the 2019 road season. Focusing on the catalan @ciclismecat "gran classics" and a series of Spanish stage races.
Not the biggest team in the world but with our tight and motivated squadra, success will be inevitable!
Hoping I can add value with my Belgian racing experience and long range diesel engine.
(also, my @mallorca312 bragging rights licence is still valid for a few months so here a shot of me crossing the finish)

